  "important_notes": [
    "PostgresDatabaseSchema in scope description maps to PostgresSchema (class is named PostgresSchema, not PostgresDatabaseSchema)",
    "No dedicated PostgresSnapshotter class found — snapshot strategies are generic debezium-connector-common classes implementing Snapshotter SPI",
    "Snapshot isolation is configured via SnapshotIsolationMode enum: SERIALIZABLE (default/deferrable), REPEATABLE_READ, READ_COMMITTED, READ_UNCOMMITTED",
    "TypeRegistry populated at startup from pg_catalog.pg_type; supports special PG types: geometry, geography, hstore, ltree, citext, tsvector, vector, halfvec, sparsevec",
    "PostgresValueConverter.of() is the factory method called by PostgresSchema.getTableSchemaBuilder()",
    "SnapshotterService aggregates Snapshotter (mode logic) + SnapshotLock (table locking) + SnapshotQuery (SELECT generation)"
  ],

